Package gameworld

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AccessibleTile
    This class represents a tile within a Room that a player can move onto or an item/challenge can be located.
    Alien
    This class represents a Alien challenge which must be befriended with a potion by the player in order to access a portal.
    BoltCutter
    This class represents a BoltCutter which must be used to unlock the vending machine.
    Bomb
    This class represents a bomb challenge which must be diffused by the player in order to access a portal.
    ChallengeItem
    This class represents a challenge that must be completed by the player to progress through the game.
    Coin
    This class represents a Coin item which a player needs to purchase a potion from the vending machine.
    Diffuser
    This class represents a Diffuser which is needed to defuse a bomb.
    Game
    This is the main class the contains the logic for game play.
    GameworldTests
    This class tests all of the gameworld logic.
    InaccessibleTile
    This class represents a tile in a Room that cannot be accessed.
    Item
    This class represents items within the game.
    OxygenTank
    This class represents an oxygen tank which can boost the oxygen level of a player.
    Player
    This class represents a player playing the game.
    Portal
    This class represents a portal which enables a player to teleport between rooms.
    Potion
    This class represents a potion that a player must use to befriend an alien.
    Room
    This class represents a room.
    SpaceShip
    This class represents the end goal for the game, a player completes the game if the spaceship is found.
    Tile
    This class represents a tile.
    VendingMachine
    This class represents a vending machine challenge which must be unlocked and passed a coin by the player in order to dispense a potion.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Direction
    This class helps to identify the orientation of game objects relative to the room as well as the direction the player is facing.
